OL,3,CBritish Engines staff on Tyneside to
OL,4,Cstrike over pay
OL,6,FThe union says workers have also faced
OL,7,Ffive years of below-inflation pay
OL,8,Fdeals which it says have amounted to
OL,9,Fan 18% drop in wages.
OL,11,FStaff will strike from Friday 24 May
OL,12,Fto Thursday 30 May, with the warning
OL,13,Fthat action will intensify if a
OL,14,Fresolution to the dispute is not found.
OL,16,FUnite says the strikes will impact
OL,17,Fsupply chains for aerospace, civil
OL,18,Fnuclear, oil and gas, defence and
OL,19,Fmarine sectors.
