OL,6,FThe union's general secretary Sharon
OL,7,FGraham said: "British Engines' workers
OL,8,Fare sick and tired of seeing their pay
OL,9,Fgo down year after year while the
OL,10,Fcompany makes millions in profits.
OL,12,F"British Engines can afford to put
OL,13,Fforward a fair deal and our members
OL,14,Fare absolutely right to strike for
OL,15,Fone. They have Unite's total support
OL,16,Fin taking industrial action for a
OL,17,Freasonable pay rise."
