OL,6,FIn response, a spokesperson for the
OL,7,Fbusinesses said: "We offer highly
OL,8,Fcompetitive salaries within the
OL,9,Fsectors that the businesses operate
OL,10,Fand believe that the proposal we have
OL,11,Fmade is fair and reasonable. Last year
OL,12,Fthe businesses awarded a 7% pay rise
OL,13,Fapplied early to provide timely
OL,14,Fsupport to all of our employees, on
OL,15,Ftop of competitive sector increases in
OL,16,Fprior years.
