OL,6,F"It is disappointing that the Unite
OL,7,Fmembers of the three businesses have
OL,8,Fchosen to undertake industrial strike
OL,9,Faction from 24 - 26 May, despite
OL,10,Fmultiple offers aimed at reaching a
OL,11,Fresolution.
OL,13,F"We remain dedicated to investing in
OL,14,Fthe businesses in terms of people,
OL,15,Fprocesses and facilities for their
OL,16,Flong-term sustainability and will
OL,17,Fcontinue to work with members to seek
OL,18,Fa resolution."
